---
import FadeIn from "../animations/FadeIn";
---

<section class="section-padding">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <FadeIn client:load direction="up">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
          Our <span class="gradient-text">Story</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Every project we deliver is focused on outcomes: performance, clarity,
          and measurable growth.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/images/about-story.png"
            alt="Protize Office"
            class="rounded-2xl w-full"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-navy"
          >
            A Decade of Innovation and Excellence
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Founded in 2011, Protize began with a simple yet powerful vision:
              to help businesses harness the power of technology to achieve
              their goals. What started as a small team of passionate developers
              has grown into a full-service IT solutions provider serving
              clients worldwide.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our journey has been marked by continuous learning, adaptation,
              and an unwavering commitment to excellence. We've successfully
              delivered over 32 projects across various industries, from
              startups to Fortune 32 companies, always maintaining our core
              values of innovation, integrity, and client success.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, Protize stands as a trusted partner for businesses seeking
              digital transformation. Our team of 20+ experts combines deep
              technical knowledge with industry experience to deliver solutions
              that don't just meet expectationsâ€”they exceed them.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>
  </div>
</section>
